<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTa65">
<l>aṅkaṟ kiṭariṉṟi yantip poḻutattu</l>
<l>maṅka viraṇiyaṉa tākattaip – poṅki</l>
<l>yariyuruva māyppiḷanta vammā ṉavaṉē</l>
<l>kariyuruvaṅ kompocittāṉ kāyntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is the father who in the form of a lion foamed</l>
<l>[and] broke open the chest of Hiraṇya, so that he died,</l>
<l>at the time of twilight, without harm to the son ,</l>
<l>he who heatedly broke off the tusk from the elephant form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
